===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act or process of [[punish]]ing, imposing and/or applying a [[sanction]].
# A [[penalty]] to punish wrongdoing, especially for [[crime]].
# A [[suffering]] by [[pain]] or [[loss]] imposed as [[retribution]]
# {{context|figuratively|lang=en}} Any [[treatment]] or experience so [[harsh]] it feels like being punished; rough handling
#: ''a vehicle that can take a lot of '''punishment'''''

